      Public key (SUPublicEDKey in Info.plist):
        MCowBQYDK2VwAyEAqrhm8RdXyYrShqr6DN/Utx73Mj2pjuuI7Kq0GqYY4Q4=

      Private key: stored in macOS Keychain or macos/ed25519-key.pem
      (KEEP PRIVATE KEY SECURE — never commit it to git!)

      =========================================================================
      How to add a new release
      =========================================================================

      After publishing a new release on GitHub with a .dmg asset:

        1. Run the appcast generator:
           ./macos/scripts/generate-appcast.sh --auto --signing-key ./macos/ed25519-key.pem

        2. This will:
           - Fetch the latest release from GitHub
           - Download the .dmg asset
           - Sign it with Ed25519
           - Add a new <item> to this appcast.xml
           - Write a JSON version to appcast.json

        3. Upload this appcast.xml to your server at:
           https://anikku.app/sparkle/appcast.xml

      =========================================================================
      Manual mode (if --auto doesn't work):
      =========================================================================

        ./macos/scripts/generate-appcast.sh \\
          --version 1.0.1 \\
          --dmg /path/to/Anikku-1.0.1.dmg \\
          --signing-key ./macos/ed25519-key.pem \\
          --appcast ./macos/src/main/resources/Sparkle/appcast.xml

      =========================================================================
    -->

